quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  58,1,Kad semiÂṀallahu kavlelletiy tucadiluke fiy zevciha ve teÅtekiy ilellahi vallahu yesmeÂṀu tehavurekuma innallahe semiyÂṀun basÄḟyrun
  58,2,Elleziyne yuzahirune minkum min nisaihim ma hunne ummehatihim in ummehatuhum ilellaiy velednehum ve innehum leyekulune munkeren minelkavli ve zuren ve innallahe leÂṀafuvvun Äafurun
  58,3,Velleziyne yuzahirune min nisaihim summe yeÂṀudune lima kalu fetahriyru rekabetin min kabli en yetemassa zalikum tuÂṀazune bihi vallahu bima taÂṀmelune habiyrun
  58,4,Femen lem yecid fesÄḟyamu Åehreyni mutetabiÂṀayni min kabli en yetemassa femen lem yestetÄḟÂṀ feÄḟtÂṀamu sittiyne miskiynen zalike lituÂṀminu billahi ve resulihi ve tilke hududullahi ve lilkafiriyne ÂṀazabun eliymun
  58,5,ÄḞnnelleziyne yuhaddunallahe ve resulehu kubitu kema kubitelleziyne min kablihim ve kad enzelna ayatin beyyinatin v uhumullahu cemiyÂṀan feyunebbiuhum bima ÂṀamilu ahsahullahu ve nesuhu e lilkafiriyne ÂṀazabun muhiynun
  58,6,Yevme yebÂṀas vallahu ÂṀala kulli ÅeyÂṀin Åehiydun
  58,7,Elem tere ennallahe yaÂṀlemu ma fiyssemavati ve ma fiylÂṀardÄḟ ma yekunu min necva selasetin illa huve rabiÂṀuhum ve la hamsetin illa huve sadisuhum ve la edna min zalike ve la eksere illa huve meÂṀahum iyne ma kanu summe yunebbiuhum bima ÂṀamilu yevmelkÄḟyameti innallahe bikulli ÅeyÂṀin ÂṀaliymun
  58,8,Elem tere ilelleziyne nuhu ÂṀaninnecva summe yeÂṀudune lima nuhu ÂṀanhu ve yetenacevne bilÂṀismi velÂṀudvani ve maÂṀsÄḟyetirresuli ve iza cauke hayyevke bima lem yuhayyike bilillahu ve yekulune fiy enfusihim lev la yuÂṀazzibunallahu bima nekulu hasbuhum cehennemu yaslevneha febi;ÂṀselmasÄḟyru
  58,9,Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza tenaceytum fela tetenacev bilÂṀismi velÂṀudvani ve maÂṀsÄḟyetirresuli ve tenacev bilbirri vettakva vettekullahelleziy ileyhi tuhÅerune
  58,10,ÄḞnnemennecva mineÅÅeytani liyahzunelleziyne amenu ve leyse bidarrihim ÅeyÂṀen illa biiznillahi ve ÂṀalellahi felyetevekkelilmuÂṀminune
  58,11,Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza kÄḟyle lekum tefessehu fiylmecalisi fefsehu yefsehÄḟllahu lekum ve iza kÄḟylenÅuzu fenÅuzu yerfeÂṀÄḟllahulleziyne amenu minkum velleziyne utulÂṀÄḟlme derecatin vallahu bima taÂṀmelune habiyrun.ÂṀ
  58,12,Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza naceytumurresule fekaddimu beyne yedey necvakum sadekaten zalike hayrun lekum ve atheru fein lem tecidu feinnallahe Äafurun rahÄḟymun
  58,13,EeÅfaktum en tukaddimu beyne yedey necvakum sadekatin feiz lem tefÂṀalu ve taballahu ÂṀaleykum feekÄḟymussalate ve atuzzekate ve etÄḟyÂṀallahe ve resulehu vallahu habiyrun bima taÂṀmelune
  58,14,Elem tere ilelleziyne tevellev kavmen ÄadÄḟballahu ÂṀaleyhim ma hum minkum ve la minhum ve yahlifune ÂṀalelkezibi ve hum yaÂṀlemune
  58,15,EÂṀaddallahu lehum ÂṀazaben Åediyden innehum sae ma lanu yaÂṀmelune
  58,16,ÄḞttehazu eymanehum cunneten fesaddu ÂṀan sebiylillahi felehum ÂṀazabun muhiynun
  58,17,Len tuÄniye ÂṀanhum emvaluhum ve la evladuhum minallahi ÅeyÂṀen ulaik ashabunnari hum fiyha halidune
  58,18,Yevme yebÂṀasuhumullahu cemiyÂṀan feyahlifune lehu kema yahlifune lekum ve yahsebune ennehum ÂṀala ÅeyÂṀin ela innehum humulkazibune
  58,19,ÄḞstahvese ÂṀaleyhimuÅÅeytanu feensahum zikrallahi ulaike hÄḟzbuÅÅeytani ela inne hÄḟzbeÅÅeytani humulhasirune
  58,20,ÄḞnnelleziyne yuhaddunallahe ve resulehu ulaike fiylÂṀezelliyne
  58,21,Ketaballahu leaÄlibenne ene ve rusuliy innallahe kaviyyun ÂṀaziyzun
  58,22,La tecidu kavmen yuÂṀminune billahi velyevmilÂṀahÄḟri yuvaddune men haddallahe ve resulehu ve lev kanu abaehum ev ebnaehum ev Äḟhvanehum ev ÂṀaÅiyretehum ulaike ketebe fiy kulubihimulÂṀiymane ve eyyedehum biruhÄḟn minhu ve yudhÄḟluhum cennatin tecriy min tahtihelÂṀenharu halidiyne fiyha radÄḟyallahu ÂṀanhum ve radu ÂṀanhu ulaike hÄḟzbullahi ela inne hÄḟzballahi humulmuflihune